ğŸ›  Technical Specifications

ğŸ§© Backend Stack

Runtime: Node.js

Framework: Express.js

ORM: Sequelize

Database: PostgreSQL

Authentication: JWT

Email Service: Resend


ğŸ¨ Frontend Stack

Framework: React 18

State Management: Redux Toolkit

Routing: React Router v6

Styling: SASS Modules

Forms: Formik + Yup Validation


Database Schema

Users: Customers, Creatives, Moderators

Contests: Active, Finished, Pending

Offers: Creative submissions with status tracking

Messages: Real-time chat system

Transactions: Payment and payout tracking


